  "text": "As mentioned before, small UAVs suffer the most from the resource constraints. In [CITATION_1] , the problem of optimal routing is studied, while the fuel constraints are taken into account. In the designed scenario, which is actually the case for most of the UAV application, the aircraft is supposed to visit several target points during its mission and refueling depots are also positioned in its way. Therefore, the goal of an optimal routing scheduling is to while the UAV fulfills its mission, it never runs out fuel.",
